|------|---------|-------|
| `/Users/kienduong/works/ai-agents/OpenACP/src/adapters/shared/message-dispatcher.ts` | Dispatcher with verbosity filtering | 17-33 (shouldDispatch), 27-59 (dispatchMessage) |
| `/Users/kienduong/works/ai-agents/OpenACP/src/adapters/discord/activity.ts` | Discord ActivityTracker, ThinkingIndicator, PlanCard, UsageMessage | 8-241 |
| `/Users/kienduong/works/ai-agents/OpenACP/src/adapters/discord/adapter.ts` | Discord adapter handlers | 517-592 (messageHandlers) |
| `/Users/kienduong/works/ai-agents/OpenACP/src/adapters/telegram/activity.ts` | Telegram ActivityTracker, ThinkingIndicator, PlanCard, UsageMessage | 9-329 |
| `/Users/kienduong/works/ai-agents/OpenACP/src/adapters/telegram/adapter.ts` | Telegram adapter handlers | 602-684 (messageHandlers) |

